sequenceDiagram
participant Client
participant API
participant Facade as HBnBFacade
participant UserRepo
participant PlaceRepo
participant Review
participant ReviewRepo
participant DB

Client->>API: POST /reviews
API->>Facade: add_review(user_id, place_id, data)
Facade->>UserRepo: get_by_id(user_id)
UserRepo->>DB: SELECT user
DB-->>UserRepo: OK
Facade->>PlaceRepo: get_by_id(place_id)
PlaceRepo->>DB: SELECT place
DB-->>PlaceRepo: OK
Facade->>Review: new Review(data)
Facade->>ReviewRepo: save(review)
ReviewRepo->>DB: INSERT review
DB-->>ReviewRepo: OK
ReviewRepo-->>Facade: saved
Facade-->>API: success
API-->>Client: 201 Created
